message.content:
@prefix : <http://example.com/env#> .
@prefix psr: <https://w3id.org/psr-task#> .
@prefix soma: <http://www.ease-crc.org/ont/SOMA.owl#> .
@prefix dul: <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#> .
@prefix geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

:KitchenDiningRoom a psr:Environment ;
    dul:hasComponent :Fridge,
                     :RangeHood,
                     :KitchenCabinet,
                     :Countertop,
                     :DiningTable,
                     :DiningChair1,
                     :DiningChair2,
                     :DiningChair3,
                     :DiningChair4,
                     :Hob,
                     :JamJar,
                     :JelloBox,
                     :Salt,
                     :RiceBubbles,
                     :ChuckyCereal,
                     :Plates,
                     :Pot,
                     :Mug,
                     :SnacksBox,
                     :FruitBowl,
                     :EvianBottle,
                     :Pitcher,
                     :WineGlass
.

:Fridge a psr:Appliance ;
    psr:hasAffordance :FridgeOpening,
                       :FridgeClosing
.

:FridgeOpening a soma:Opening .
:FridgeClosing a soma:Closing .

:RangeHood a psr:Appliance .

:KitchenCabinet a psr:Furniture .

:Countertop a psr:Furniture .

:DiningTable a psr:Furniture .

:DiningChair1 a psr:Furniture .
:DiningChair2 a psr:Furniture .
:DiningChair3 a psr:Furniture .
:DiningChair4 a psr:Furniture .

:Hob a psr:Appliance .

:JamJar a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_JamJar
.

:Loc_JamJar a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:JelloBox a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_JelloBox
.

:Loc_JelloBox a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:Salt a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_Salt
.

:Loc_Salt a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:RiceBubbles a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_RiceBubbles
.

:Loc_RiceBubbles a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:ChuckyCereal a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_ChuckyCereal
.

:Loc_ChuckyCereal a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:Plates a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_Plates
.

:Loc_Plates a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:Pot a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_Pot ;
    psr:hasAffordance :PotPickingUp
.

:Loc_Pot a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Hob
.

:PotPickingUp a soma:PickingUp .

:Mug a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_Mug ;
    psr:hasAffordance :MugPickingUp
.

:Loc_Mug a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :Countertop
.

:MugPickingUp a soma:PickingUp .

:SnacksBox a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_SnacksBox
.

:Loc_SnacksBox a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :DiningTable
.

:FruitBowl a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_FruitBowl
.

:Loc_FruitBowl a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :DiningTable
.

:EvianBottle a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_EvianBottle
.

:Loc_EvianBottle a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :DiningTable
.

:Pitcher a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_Pitcher
.

:Loc_Pitcher a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :DiningTable
.

:WineGlass a psr:Object ;
    dul:hasLocation :Loc_WineGlass
.

:Loc_WineGlass a psr:CurrentLocation ;
    psr:onTopOf :DiningTable
.
